=Introduction=

The Price viewpoint enables to simply describe the non-functional aspect of price in Capella.
It provides several capabilities:

* Definition of price value to be associated with model elements
* Definition of maximum price value to be associated with model elements
* Computation of model element price value based on self price value and child price values
* Visualization of maximum price value compliance with regards to computed value